	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>The [[lookup @name lowercase]] locks eyes with one humanoid it can see within 30 feet. If the target can see the [[lookup @name lowercase]], the creature must make a <strong>DC 17 Wisdom</strong> saving throw or become charmed.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save wis]]{Wisdom Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target regards the [[lookup @name lowercase]] as a trusted friend, defends it, and acts favorably toward requests and actions (including bite attacks) without being forced.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect, but the creature is aware that it resisted the magic.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Maintaining the Charm:</strong> The effect lasts 24 hours unless the [[lookup @name lowercase]] is destroyed, on another plane, or it uses a bonus action to end it. If the [[lookup @name lowercase]] or its allies harm the target, the target can repeat the saving throw immediately, ending the effect on a success.</p>",
